port forwarding 의 표준 패턴. 외부 8888 트래픽을 내부 web 으로 매핑하고, conntrack
table 에서 orig dst (fw IP) 와 reply src (web IP) 가 다른 것을 통해 NAT 변환
흔적을 식별한다. 마지막에 cleanup 까지 1 cycle.

## 💻 실행 명령

```bash
# 1. DNAT 룰 추가 (prerouting)
ssh 6v6-fw 'sudo nft add rule ip six_nat prerouting iifname "eth0" tcp dport 8888 \
    counter dnat to 10.20.32.80:80'

# 2. fw 자체로 들어오는 8888/tcp 허용 (DNAT 평가 후 routing 결정 → input/forward 분기)
ssh 6v6-fw 'sudo nft insert rule inet six_filter input position 0 tcp dport 8888 accept'

# 3. attacker 에서 fw:8888 으로 curl
ssh 6v6-attacker 'curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}\n" \
    -H "Host: juice.6v6.lab" http://10.20.30.1:8888/'

# 4. conntrack 의 양방향 변환 확인
ssh 6v6-fw 'sudo conntrack -L 2>/dev/null | grep "dport=8888" | head -1'

# 5. nft counter 증가 확인
ssh 6v6-fw 'sudo nft list chain ip six_nat prerouting | grep -B1 "dport 8888"'

# 6. Cleanup
HANDLE=$(ssh 6v6-fw 'sudo nft -a list chain ip six_nat prerouting | \
    grep "dport 8888" | grep -oE "handle [0-9]+" | head -1 | awk "{print \$2}"')
[ -n "$HANDLE" ] && ssh 6v6-fw "sudo nft delete rule ip six_nat prerouting handle $HANDLE"

HANDLE2=$(ssh 6v6-fw 'sudo nft -a list chain inet six_filter input | \
    grep "dport 8888" | grep -oE "handle [0-9]+" | head -1 | awk "{print \$2}"')
[ -n "$HANDLE2" ] && ssh 6v6-fw "sudo nft delete rule inet six_filter input handle $HANDLE2"
```

