PROMPT: ## 🎯 MISSION — suricata.yaml 의 핵심 4 키 점검 (af-packet / rule-files / eve-log / HOME_NET)

Suricata 의 정책 본체 4 키. af-packet 미정의 = sniff 불가, rule-files 미정의 = 탐지
불가, eve-log 미정의 = 분석 불가, HOME_NET 부정확 = 룰 macro 오작동.

## 💻 실행 명령

```bash
# 1. af-packet 두 NIC + cluster-id + cluster-type
ssh 6v6-ips 'sudo grep -A6 "^af-packet:" /etc/suricata/suricata.yaml | head -20'

# 2. default-rule-path + rule-files
ssh 6v6-ips 'sudo grep -B1 -A5 "^rule-files:" /etc/suricata/suricata.yaml | head -10'
ssh 6v6-ips 'sudo grep "^default-rule-path:" /etc/suricata/suricata.yaml'

# 3. eve-log enabled + types
ssh 6v6-ips 'sudo grep -A10 "^outputs:" /etc/suricata/suricata.yaml | head -15'

# 4. HOME_NET / EXTERNAL_NET
ssh 6v6-ips 'sudo grep -A2 "address-groups:" /etc/suricata/suricata.yaml | head -10'

# 5. syntax 검증 (변경 안 했으므로 OK 이어야 함)
ssh 6v6-ips 'sudo suricata -T -c /etc/suricata/suricata.yaml 2>&1 | tail -3'
```

