+ ModSec 두 source) → **Purple** 의 우선순위 + Active Response 권장.

## 💻 실행 명령

```bash
# 1. baseline
BEFORE=$(ssh 6v6-siem 'sudo wc -l /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json | awk "{print \$1}"')
echo "baseline: $BEFORE"

# 2. Red — 5 XSS burst
echo "=== Red 5 XSS ==="
for i in 1 2 3 4 5; do
  code=$(ssh 6v6-attacker "curl -s -o /dev/null -w '%{http_code}' -H 'Host: juice.6v6.lab' 'http://10.20.30.1/?q=<script>alert($i)</script>'")
  echo "  burst $i → $code"
done
sleep 8

# 3. Blue — alerts.json delta
AFTER=$(ssh 6v6-siem 'sudo wc -l /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json | awk "{print \$1}"')
DELTA=$((AFTER - BEFORE))
echo "Blue: delta = $DELTA (예상 5 ~ 15 — Suricata 양 NIC + ModSec audit)"

# 4. Blue — 최근 alert 의 rule.id 분포
echo "=== rule.id 분포 (delta 만) ==="
ssh 6v6-siem "sudo tail -$DELTA /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json 2>/dev/null | jq -r '.rule.id' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -10"

# 5. Blue — agent.name 분포
echo "=== agent 분포 ==="
ssh 6v6-siem "sudo tail -$DELTA /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json 2>/dev/null | jq -r '.agent.name' | sort | uniq -c"

# 6. Blue — level 분포
echo "=== level 분포 ==="
ssh 6v6-siem "sudo tail -$DELTA /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json 2>/dev/null | jq -r '.rule.level' | sort | uniq -c"

# 7. Purple — 권장
echo
echo "=== Purple 권장 ==="
cat <<'EOF'
1. level 격상 — local_rules.xml 의 rule override (Suricata XSS → level 7)
2. Active Response — level 7+ 시 attacker IP nftables drop set 추가
3. dashboard 의 Suricata + ModSec panel 통합 (W10)
4. integratord 활성 — Slack 알림
5. CDB list — known attacker IP 자동 분류
EOF
```

## 📋 확인 사항

- delta 5+ (Suricata 양 NIC × 5 = 10 + ModSec audit 5 = 15 가능)
