PROMPT: ## 🎯 MISSION — **R/B/P** XSS 5 burst → 5 source dashboard 통합

**Red** 5 XSS → **Blue** 5 source alert (Suricata / ModSec / Apache access log /
osquery / syscheck) 통합 추적 → **Purple** dashboard 권장.

## 💻 실행 명령

```bash
BEFORE=$(ssh 6v6-siem 'sudo wc -l /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json | awk "{print \$1}"')
echo "baseline: $BEFORE"

# Red 5 burst
echo "=== Red 5 XSS ==="
for i in 1 2 3 4 5; do
  code=$(ssh 6v6-attacker "curl -s -o /dev/null -w '%{http_code}' -H 'Host: juice.6v6.lab' 'http://10.20.30.1/?q=<script>alert($i)</script>'")
  echo "  burst $i → $code"
done
sleep 10

# Blue — alerts.json delta + source 분석
AFTER=$(ssh 6v6-siem 'sudo wc -l /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json | awk "{print \$1}"')
DELTA=$((AFTER - BEFORE))
echo "Blue: delta = $DELTA"

# rule.groups 분포 (source 별)
echo
echo "=== source 분포 ==="
ssh 6v6-siem "sudo tail -$DELTA /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json 2>/dev/null | jq -r '.rule.groups | join(\",\")' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -10"

# agent.name 분포
echo
echo "=== agent 분포 ==="
ssh 6v6-siem "sudo tail -$DELTA /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json 2>/dev/null | jq -r '.agent.name' | sort | uniq -c"

# rule.id top 5
echo
echo "=== rule.id top 5 ==="
ssh 6v6-siem "sudo tail -$DELTA /var/ossec/logs/alerts/alerts.json 2>/dev/null | jq -r '.rule.id' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -5"

# Purple — dashboard 권장
echo
echo "=== Purple 권장 5 ==="
cat <<'EOF'
1. Discovery panel — rule.level >= 5 default filter
2. Saved search — XSS 공격 패턴 (rule.id 86xxx OR 30xxx)
3. Modules > Security events — 시간 별 timeline
4. MITRE ATT&CK panel — T1190 매핑
5. RBAC — analyst 권한으로 SOC tier 1 access
EOF
```

